this is a finance transaction react native expo application targeted at the Egyptain Market where it is designed to help
users navigate their finances like Pros. the core of the app has all the features a normal finance app has
the unique addition is "Ameen" the AI agent that will have access to the user finance info in the app and help
the user budget, save money, pay debts and overall have healthier finances.

Here are some rules while developing:
- for the microcopy we need to have a localized arabic and english versions
- if we are building a new screen we breakdown the screen elements into components, components do not need to be overlly generic or too specific they just need to fit the job
